                        ;************************************
                        ;* Demo using my speaker/switch
                        ;* board.
                        ;*
                        ;* Schematic provided in folder
                        ;* Switchs must go to 5v and GND, 
                        ;* not GND and float.
                        ;* 
                        ;* Adapted from the demo in the
                        ;* KIM-1 manual.
                        ;*
                        ;* NOTE: The sound is SUPER SUPER
                        ;* quiet.  I suspect its because
                        ;* the Altaid is vampiring the voltage
                        ;* from the board.
                        ;************************************
                        
   2000                 			ORG 	2000H
   2000   06 00         INIT: 		MVI	 	B,0			; Set B to initial value of 0
   2002   04            START: 		INR 	B			; Toggle Speaker
   2003   78            			MOV	 	A,B	
   2004   d3 61         			OUT 	61H	 
   2006   db 60         			IN 		60H		; Read buttons
   2008   0f            			RRC		
   2009   e6 7f         			ANI		7FH
   200b   00            DELAY: 		NOP
   200c   00            			NOP
   200d   00            			NOP
   200e   3d            			DCR		A			; Delay by an amount specified
   200f   f2 0b 20      			JP		DELAY		; by the count in A
   2012   fa 02 20      			JM		START		; Go Start
   2015                 			END
200b  DELAY         2000  INIT          2002  START         
